These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Sport: tennis, weightlifting, biathlon
1. Sport:weightlifting is on the right of Sport:biathlon##1
2. Sport:tennis is on the far right##1
3. Sport:tennis is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | biathlon | weightlifting | tennis |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Food: peas, pomegranate, broccoli
1. Food:pomegranate is in an odd position##4
2. Food:peas is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | peas | broccoli | pomegranate |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Hobby: traveling, singing, writing
1. Hobby:singing is in an even position##4
2. Hobby:singing is on the left or right of Hobby:writing##3
3. Hobby:writing is on the right of Hobby:singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | traveling | singing | writing |

 #################################
 
